import React from 'react'
import Tab from 'react-bootstrap/Tab'
import Tabs from 'react-bootstrap/Tabs'

import StudentLogin from './student-login.component'
import InstructorLogin from './instructor-login.component'
import CreateStudentAccount from '../../components/student/student-create-account.component'
import CreateInstructorAccount from './instructor-create-account.component'

function Card (props) {
  return props.type === "student" ?
  (
    <Card style={{ width: '18rem' }}>
      <Card.Body>
        <Card.Title>Cheat Checker for Students</Card.Title>

      </Card.Body>
    </Card>
  )
  : (
    <Tabs defaultActiveKey={props.defaultTab} id="uncontrolled-tab-example">
      <Tab eventKey="instructorLogin" title="Login">
        <StudentLogin />
      </Tab>
      <Tab eventKey="instructorCreateAccount" title="Create Account" disabled>
        <CreateInstructorAccount />
      </Tab>
    </Tabs>
  )
}

export default Card
